      <title>WSL Ubuntu22.04默认用户（default用户）更改_wsl ubuntu切换用户-CSDN博客</title>
      <link href="/2025/02/20/250215~WSL%20Ubuntu22.04%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%EF%BC%88default%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%EF%BC%89%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9_wsl%20ubuntu%E5%88%87%E6%8D%A2%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7-CSDN%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
      <url>/2025/02/20/250215~WSL%20Ubuntu22.04%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%EF%BC%88default%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%EF%BC%89%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9_wsl%20ubuntu%E5%88%87%E6%8D%A2%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7-CSDN%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul><li>WSL Ubuntu22.04默认用户（default用户）更改 <blockquote><p>管理员权限打开powershell，关掉子系统</p><p><code>wsl --shutdown</code></p><p>设置默认用户 </p><p><code>&lt;wsl&gt; config --default-user &lt;username&gt;</code></p><p><img src="https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/blog_migrate/cdacdeca8f5b3bd47fa4bac5881aaf4a.png"></p><p>此时再打开wsl ubuntu, 默认用户更改成功<br><img src="https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/blog_migrate/150fd74a62802b4469026191ca83d825.png"></p></blockquote></li></ul><h1 id="致谢">1. 致谢</h1><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/single_musketeer/article/details/130309835">https://blog.csdn.net/single_musketeer/article/details/130309835</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
